description:
How can we learn to trust God from the story of Moses in Numbers 20? Why did God instruct Moses to speak to the Rock? How can we follow God's command to speak to the Rock? Can the story of Moses speaking to the Rock tell us something about our personal relationship with God?

In this presentation, Pastor Walter Veith explores numerous Bible accounts of people who spoke to the Rock. What did these people learn when they did? How did speaking to the Rock strengthen their relationship with God? 

Discover how you can better trust God and draw closer to Him. Learn what it means to speak to the Rock!
